//
// Lightweight fiber/coroutine implementation:
//   - Stackful coroutines with configurable stack sizes
//   - Symmetric and asymmetric transfer
//   - Work-stealing scheduler integration
//   - Guard pages for stack overflow detection
//   - Platform-specific context switching
//
